Test scenario: Signup

TC_1
Test case: user is able to create account successfully
Test steps:
1. Go to AUT
2. Go to signup modal window
3. Enter username and password
4. Verify the account is created and logged in

TC_2
Test case: sign up with empty username and password
Test steps:
1. Go to AUT
2. Go to signup modal window
3. Do not enter anything into username and password
4. Verify that system displays a message "Please fill out Username and Password.".

TC_3
Test case: sign up with an existing account
Test steps:
1. Go to AUT
2. Go to signup modal window
3. Create an account that already exists in the system
4. Verify that system displays a message as "This user already exist.".